descriptionHtml:
Have you ever thought that daggers in skyrim swing a bit too slow for their size and weight? well this mod fixes that problem and now your daggers will swing noticeably faster.

right now this mod only works for vanilla but i am working on a way to make it compatible with reversed daggers mod

daggers now swing 55% faster

----------CHANGELOG----------

1.0.1
- changed speed percentage to 55%
- changed damage so daggers now do slightly less damage than swords

1.0.0
- made daggers swing faster
author: Jozzarozzer
